title: Leave Your Burden, Down By The River Side,
lyrics:
Leave your burden, down by the river side,
Down by the river side,
Down by the river side,
Leave your burden, down by the river side,
Carry them no more,
I say carry them no more,
Carry them no more. Carry them no more
I say to carry them no more,
Carry them no more,
Carry them no more.
